data.description: Welcome to Eagles Crossing! This beautiful ranch home sits on a quiet 2.4-acre wooded lot in the back of the subdivision. This spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath is filled with custom features. In the fenced-in backyard, you will discover a nice deck to enjoy your coffee or grill, a pool to relax in when it's hot, or a sit by the fire pit when it is cold. Inside has several custom accent walls, trim, and fireplace. All of the following items were updated in 2018: fridge/freezer, stove, microwave, dishwasher, HVAC, garage door opener, dryer, and kitchen cabinets. There is plenty of extra storage to include: two hidden safes, two attic accesses, and cabinets installed in the garage. The Master on Main suite has a double vanity, separate tub and shower, as well as a spacious walk-in closet. This house is conveniently located to Loganville, and centrally located between Highway 316 and 78. Seller is willing to contribute up to 2.5% towards loan buy down with full price offer.
